efinition","text":"n.越位"}]},{"number":1195,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"score a goal 射门得分","headword":"score a goal"},{"type":"entry","text":"time-out [ˈtaɪm aʊt]","headword":"time-out"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.（球类比赛进行中的）暂停"},{"type":"entry","text":"false ball 假球","headword":"false ball"},{"type":"entry","text":"black whistle 黑哨","headword":"black whistle"},{"type":"section","text":"Step2 学以致用"},{"type":"section","text":"Conversation 1"},{"type":"example","text":"A：Did you hurt yourself in the soccer game?（你在足球比赛中受伤"},{"type":"text","text":"了？）"},{"type":"example","text":"B：Yeah, my left ankle is swollen.（是的，我的左脚踝肿了。）"},{"type":"section","text":"Conversation 2"},{"type":"example","text":"A：Hey, Ashley, what's up?（嗨，阿什利，有事吗？）"},{"type":"example","text":"B：There's a hockey game on Friday. I want you to come.（周五有场"},{"type":"text","text":"曲棍球比赛，我想让你来。）"},{"type":"section","text":"Conversation 3"},{"type":"example","text":"A：What are you doing? It looks like you're beating each other up!"},{"type":"text","text":"（你们在干什么？看起来像是在互相打斗。）"}]},{"number":1196,"blocks":[{"type":"example","text":"B：We are playing rugby.（我们在打橄榄球。）"}]}]}